                "invention-title": [
                    "Equipment stabilizing device for producing hydrogen by electrolyzing water on offshore platform and control method of equipment stabilizing device",
                    "一种用于海上平台电解水制氢的设备稳定装置及其控制方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to an equipment stabilizing device for water electrolysis hydrogen production of an offshore platform and a control method of the equipment stabilizing device. The equipment stabilizing device mainly comprises a hydrogen production container, a car, a middle frame, an outer supporting frame, a Y-shaped supporting rod, a spring damper, a tension sensor, a water tank, a water pump, a reversing valve, a water pipe and a bearing seat. A hydrogen production container and a water tank are installed on a car, the car is installed on a middle frame, the middle frame is installed on an outer supporting frame, and outer supporting frame stand columns are installed on an offshore platform; y-shaped supporting rods provided with spring dampers are arranged on a front cross beam and a rear cross beam at the upper part of the car and connected with the middle frame; y-shaped supporting rods provided with spring dampers are arranged on a left cross beam and a right cross beam of the middle frame and connected with the outer supporting frame, and tension sensors are arranged on the spring dampers; rolling and pitching of the car are reduced through spring damping; the tension sensor senses the posture of the car and controls the reversing valve to adjust the water pumping waterway flow direction of the water pump so as to change the liquid level of the water tank and adjust the gravity center of the car, and the water electrolysis hydrogen production equipment used for the offshore platform keeps stable."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种用于海上平台电解水制氢的设备稳定装置及其控制方法，主要包括制氢集装箱、轿箱、中框架、外支撑框架、Y形撑杆、弹簧阻尼、拉力传感器、水箱、水泵、换向阀、水管、轴承座。本发明制氢集装箱和水箱安装在轿箱上，轿箱安装在中框架，中框架安装在外支撑框架，外支撑框架立柱安装在海上平台上；轿箱上部前后横粱上设有装有弹簧阻尼的Y形撑杆与中框架连接；中框架左右横梁上设有装有弹簧阻尼的Y形撑杆与外支撑框架连接，弹簧阻尼上装有拉力传感器；通过弹簧阻尼减轻轿箱的横摇和纵摇；通过拉力传感器感知轿箱姿态，控制换向阀调整水泵抽水的水路流向，以改变水箱液位，调整轿箱重心，使用于海上平台的电解水制氢设备保持稳定。"
                }
